[       ] profile and optimize a few core functions: SA, UA

[ 0.8.5 ] non-overlapping/overlapping Schwarz smoother
[       ] replace Schwarz smoother by a C version
[       ] polynomial smoothers -- 1/x and Chevbshev (Xiaozhe)
[       ] Tarjan algorithm and other orderings (Ludmil and Xiaozhe)
